<section id="certinfo-rn-overview"><title>Component Overview</title>
    
    <!-- This is where you describe the information provider (pulled into both the release notes and the reference page). 
    This should be simply one paragraph, so paste your text in between the para tags below. -->
    
    <para>
    This provider will monitor the life of a remote certificate.  It
    connects to an ssl TCP listener and obtains the certificate from
    it.  If then checks the cert for subject, start date, end data,
    and email address.  All of this information is put in the index if
    it is successfully obtained.
    </para>

</section>
